%h3.text-uppercase #{@brand.name} color palette
%p The Light Reaction color palette is formed by three groups of colors with different roles in the visual system.
%p The Bright Palette is what makes the brand recognizable and brings in the light aspect of Light Reaction. The Bright Palette is formed by the Light Reaction Yellow, used in the logo, and three other warm colors.
%p The Grays group is made up of three different shades of gray, bringing a powerful contrast when combined with the Bright Palette.
%p The Blue Accent group brings three different shades of blue to the palette. It should be used in small proportions in layouts or as an additional color in charts and graphs.
